column2: Angela gifts Dwight the bobblehead; he gives her a key to his house
column3: "My animal deserves a lot of loving," Dwight's incredibly chauvinistic way of saying Angela matters to him
column4: Jim wishes Pam a happy Valentine's Day with a practiced casualness. John Krasinski delivers the line perfectly, in a way that you know Jim spent all day thinking of how to say it just right. How to seem like a friend while half-hiding what he truly wants.
